notes: Tissue type: Cell Culture, Fibroblast, Skin, Unspecified; Remarks: Indian muntjac. Culture was established from explants of a skin biopsy. Cell morphology is fibroblast-like. Culture was frozen  5 passages after receipt of culture at CCR. The karyotype is 7,XY with 4% of the cells examined showing random chromosome loss/gain and 6% showing random chromosomal aberrations.
